>The Top 25 Books for 2025</a> • <em>Artforum&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.artforum.com/lists/best-of-books-2025/chika-okeke-agulu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best of 2025: Books</a> • <em>Harper&#8217;s Bazaar&#8217;s <a href="https://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/art-books-music/g69663894/best-books-of-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The 10 Best Books of 2025</a> • Libby&#8217;s <a href="https://www.libbylife.com/blog/the-best-books-of-2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Best Books of 2025</a> • <em>The Observer&#8217;s</em> </em> <a href="https://observer.co.uk/culture/books/article/writers-recommend-the-best-books-of-2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Writers Recommend: The Best Books of 2025</a> • <em>The Paris Review&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.theparisreview.org/blog/2025/12/12/our-favorite-books-of-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Our Favorite Books of 2025</a> • Shelf Awareness&#8217;s <a href="https://www.shelf-awareness.com/sar-issue.html?issue=1318" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">2025 Best Books of the Year</a> • <em>The Telegraph&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/books/authors/best-books-of-2025/#fiction" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Greatest Books of 2025</a> • California Review of Books&#8217; <a href="https://calirb.com/10-best-books-of-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">10 Best Books of 2025</a> • Booklist&#8217;s <a href="https://www.booklistonline.com/Booklist-s-Editors-Choice-Adult-Books-2025/pid=9818458" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Editors’ Choice: Adult Books, 2025</a> • <em>The Times&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.thetimes.com/culture/books/article/best-books-2025-new-christmas-fiction-q6fclgvvr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Best Books of 2025</a> • <em>The Chicago Tribune&#8217;s</em> <a href="https://www.chicagotribune.com/2025/12/03/the-10-best-books-of-2025-censorship-crime-and-compassion/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The 10 Best Books of 2025</a> • The Conversation&#8217;s <a href="https://theconversation.com/best-books-of-2025-our-experts-share-their-picks-268875" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Best Books of 2025</a> • PBS&#8217;s <a href="https://www.pbs.org/newshour/arts/14-best-book-of-2025-according-to-these-experts" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">14 Best Books of 2025</a> • BookPage&#8217;s <a href="https://www.bookpage.com/best-books/best-fiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Best Fiction of 2025</a> and <a href="https://www.bookpage.com/best-books/best-nonfiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Best Nonfiction of 2025</a> • and of course, Lit Hub&#8217;s <a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-43-favorite-books-of-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">43 Favorite Books of 2025</a></p>
